{"tid":1273784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我提醒多次各位鍵盤戰士","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:03:06.000Z","uid":72301,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1635575749c3348158a73229a05f8c97d363e4e0","tid":1273784,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"明白大家都係關心義士<br />\n要記住你地有<span style=\"color: red;\">陳述</span>現場情況嘅權利<br />\n但千祈唔好加你主觀嘅意願同提議落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以提義士邊度有狗 政府果邊有咩消息<br />\n但唔好自己為人地判斷走/留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打仗最重要軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住有可能因為你一個主觀留言累輸成場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位加油 小心</span>"},{"pid":"5ccf17bad4e1f22c86a11d2e1b295551f5f07125","tid":1273784,"uid":13984,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2300開記招全部記者2300去主席台</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fad51115cb4417f0a9cabaea031f20d6bf8577d","tid":1273784,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95461f8407c39e89d9c535d237792af1cd518cff","tid":1273784,"uid":50414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d63994a1a69ced6e88f661bd7d573b58032bfab6","tid":1273784,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4b8de6b3361113cd70a0b0edf241e338106eb6b","tid":1273784,"uid":271413,"like":0,"disli